{"tid":1420080,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"記招呢樣野做得好好！","createTime":"2019-08-06T03:36:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T04:11:23.000Z","uid":51171,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ef54de94fea87601c3a69f8acc8dea91297fae6f","tid":1420080,"uid":51171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:36:37.000Z","msg":"希望keep住追擊政府&amp;佢地嘅記者會，將真相同埋市民嘅心聲講返出黎，唔好俾佢一言堂。<br />\n<br />\nbtw, <span style=\"color: red;\">一定要keep住有英文 version</span>。原因如下：<br />\n<br />\n1.將聲音帶向國際社會。<br />\n<br />\n2.呢點好膚淺，但真實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：講英文會令中老年嗰班改觀，佢地會覺得你地有返咁上下文化、知識、智慧(因為佢地唔識英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，慢慢洗去「班靚仔貪得意搞亂」嘅形象。以前都有社運人士講英文，但唔及恆常嘅記者會咁大功效。"},{"pid":"9604a5ccd746f05b58c760a04b5fe514c037284e","tid":1420080,"uid":118125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:38:28.000Z","msg":"總之唔可以比黑警記者會係咁一言堂洗腦"},{"pid":"32a882176c899ecf1356d7fe4207471a2aeef2a4","tid":1420080,"uid":279000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:38:47.000Z","msg":"最好係喺差佬記招之後開 可以迅速還撃"},{"pid":"6eb4fe5f4572fd13ff6df2737bae53562420ead7","tid":1420080,"uid":90521,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:39:29.000Z","msg":"真心話用外語講更加真心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da320bfbb3077acecb5e3ec5c921ce5a5022373f","tid":1420080,"uid":51171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:40:29.000Z","msg":"支持！"},{"pid":"3f76776893937f9a72724e120dc747f9be8b94ed","tid":1420080,"uid":118125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32a882176c899ecf1356d7fe4207471a2aeef2a4","tid":1420080,"uid":279000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:38:47.000Z","msg":"最好係喺差佬記招之後開 可以迅速還撃"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:47:21.000Z","msg":"咁各有各好既....<br />\n趁政府冇記者會, 傳媒可以先報道一排,賣廣告咁有咁耐宣傳咁耐, 吸引市民注意先<br />\n如果政府開記者會之後先開,冇錯你可以針對政府觀點還擊, <br />\n但傳媒報道篇幅唔會好大, 因為報道版面一定集中番政府既記者會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d04ae4462dca6a1b8e2ecc1d2ecc37cb0f0eb7dd","tid":1420080,"uid":2757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:54:29.000Z","msg":"夜晚用差佬記者會edit返啲真相video入去踢爆佢哋啲大話，日夜夾攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cef9a533ae23defe92f7a5401b5c67a49bf42228","tid":1420080,"uid":51171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:00:11.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"86e7cf75664bba08636b8d7bf0d14b022e42852e","tid":1420080,"uid":51171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:11:23.000Z","msg":"十卜"}]}